LV-1 subtype F strain very similar to the STLV-1 strains present in such monkeys.\nCONCLUSIONS: These results strongly suggest ongoing direct zoonotic acquisition of STLV-1 in humans through severe NHP bites during hunting activities.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Filippone, Claudia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Betsem, Edouard", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Tortevoye, Patricia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Cassar, Olivier", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bassot, Sylviane", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Froment, Alain", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fontanet, Arnaud", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gessain, Antoine", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Adult", "Animals", "Antibodies, Viral", "Bites and Stings", "Blotting, Western", "Cameroon", "Cross-Sectional Studies", "Female", "HTLV-1/STLV-1", "HTLV-I Infections", "Humans", "Male", "Middle Aged", "Occupational Diseases", "Primates", "Risk Factors", "Seroepidemiologic Studies", "nonhuman primates", "severe bite", "viral cross-species transmission", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/a956f45f1208878ba9205e3ca6059c16", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/27861a2d34ffb01b2baceb9c9332b7d7a077eb73fb35e0e17afeba139750c5a6", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/SNT4826F", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/SNT4826F", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/9db344b7ddff318234baab778e8dd15c!/b246191-248778", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "do